  "texts": [
    "A support system encourages educators to learn from each other's experiences and to continuously adapt their methods and strategies as the field of AI evolves.",
    "On the other hand, some educators who realized the vast benefits arising from the use of ChatGPT and ADWTs in teaching and learning suggest ensuring all students and teachers, regardless of their background or resources, are provided equal access to these tools.",
    "This underscores the importance of providing AI tools and creating systems that allow for equitable access.",
    "Our findings corroborate some of the recommendations made by the European Network for Academic Integrity (ENAI).",
    "ENAI is an international association that brings together educational stakeholders and acts as a gatekeeper of academic integrity."
  ],
